=== About Me ===

My name is Manal Lamine, also known as Geekette. I am a Tunisian technology enthousiast who love crazy about coding and new technolgy, i have some innovations in medical  field.

I have heard about a Tunisian community in 2009 and I started following the community since then.<<BR>>
My first contribution was in Software Freedom Day 2010. And since my journey with Ubuntu-TN have started and I learned a lot about Ubuntu, FOSS and the community.<<BR>>
I have been approved as a FreedomFighter member of Ubuntu-TN community in 2011 and joined the management comity (Technical) board in 2011.
